in the cross hairs -

34
00:03:07,647 --> 00:03:09,604
- and take them down.

35
00:03:09,647 --> 00:03:14,388
Just remember:
They can buy anything, -

36
00:03:14,475 --> 00:03:18,388
- but they can't buy backbone.

37
00:03:18,432 --> 00:03:20,563
Don't let them forget that.

38
00:03:20,649 --> 00:03:22,563
