right about Rushmore.

54
00:04:13,225 --> 00:04:15,138
Come on, Dirk.

55
00:04:17,442 --> 00:04:20,401
- What's his name again?
- Max Fischer.

56
00:04:21,617 --> 00:04:23,574
Sharp little guy.

57
00:04:26,140 --> 00:04:29,576
