I got into this school?

75
00:06:36,251 --> 00:06:37,338
Yes.

76
00:06:37,382 --> 00:06:40,469
- You wrote a play.
- That's right.

77
00:06:40,556 --> 00:06:44,557
Second grade.
A little one act about Watergate.

78
00:06:44,644 --> 00:06:47,079
And my mother read it
and felt I should go to Rushmore.

79
00:06:47,123 --> 00:06:50,210
And you read it, and
you gave me a scholarship, didn't you?

80
00:06:50,297 --> 00:06:52,384
Mm-hmm.

81
00:06:52,471 --> 00:06:55,255
- Do you regret it?
- No, I don't regret it.

82
00:06:55,299 --> 00:06:58,125
But I still might
have to expel you.

83
00:06:58,168 --> 00:07:00,125
Couldn't...

84
00:07:00,168 --> 00:07:02,864
