Try and pull some strings
with the administration, I guess.

90
00:07:22,259 --> 00:07:24,521
Did you hear they're teaching
Japanese next year?

91
00:07:24,607 --> 00:07:26,520
That's the rumor.

92
00:07:26,608 --> 00:07:28,478
And they're canceling Latin.

93
00:07:28,566 --> 00:07:30,479
What?

94
00:07:30,565 --> 00:07:33,218
I tried to get Latin
canceled for five years.

95
00:07:33,261 --> 00:07:35,697
"It's a dead language",
I'd always say.

96
00:07:35,783 --> 00:07:38,393
Well, I guess
they finally heard you.

97
00:07:53,614 --> 00:07:55,092
Excuse me.

98
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:58,223
Could I please see a list
of all the people -

