already banged her by now.

138
00:10:18,510 --> 00:10:20,423
What?

139
00:10:20,510 --> 00:10:23,249
Just tell that deformed Scottish gorilla
to shut his fat face.

140
00:10:25,597 --> 00:10:28,163
That's my best friend's mother
he's talking about.

141
00:10:28,251 --> 00:10:30,729
I always thought that's why
you picked Dirk as your chapel partner.

142
00:10:30,816 --> 00:10:32,860
What are you, a lawyer?

143
00:10:32,903 --> 00:10:36,860
Hey, Mr. Blume.
Hey, it's Max Fischer.

144
00:10:36,947 --> 00:10:39,470
- Oh, hi.
Hey, Max, my mom just showed up.

145
00:10:39,513 --> 00:10:41,470
Is it okay if I leave early? Over.

146
00:10:41,514 --> 00:10:43,471
Sure, Charlie.

147
00:10:48,253 --> 00:10:51,212
What's the secret, Max?

148
00:10:51,254 --> 00:10:53,037
- "The secret"?
- Yeah.

149
00:10:53,125 --> 00:10:56,560
Well, you seem to have it
pretty figured out.

150
00:10:56,604 --> 00:10:58,908
The secret.
I don't know. Uh...

151
00:10:58,994 --> 00:11:01,256
I think you just gotta find
something you love to do, -

152
00:11:01,344 --> 00:11:04,866
- and then do it
for the rest of your life.

153
00:11:04,953 --> 00:11:07,562
For me, it's going to Rushmore.

154
00:11:07,648 --> 00:11:10,301
Shotgun.

155
00:11:10,388 --> 00:11:13,998
- Hey, Ronny. Hey, Donny. How you guys...
- Get in the back.

156
00:11:14,042 --> 00:11:16,216
- I said, "Shotgun".
- Get in the back, Donny.

157
00:11:17,955 --> 00:11:20,172
Let's go.

158
00:11:22,478 --> 00:11:25,044
Did you invite that kid
to your party?

159
00:11:25,130 --> 00:11:26,044
Max Fischer?

160
00:11:26,044 --> 00:11:27,566
Come on, Dad. There's
gonna be girls there.

161
00:11:27,652 --> 00:11:30,392
- I'd rather die.
- Pull your head out of your ass.

162
00:11:32,393 --> 00:11:34,915
- Good night, Mr. Littlejeans.
- Good night, Max.

163
00:11:35,002 --> 00:11:36,959
I'll see you tomorrow.

164
00:11:44,830 --> 00:11:46,917
May I see the back, please?

165
00:11:48,004 --> 00:11:49,917
Certainly.

166
00:11:52,135 --> 00:11:54,048
How's that?

167
00:11:54,136 --> 00:11:57,267
Thank you.

168
00:11:57,354 --> 00:12:01,268
I need a signature
on this geometry test, by the way.

169
00:12:01,354 --> 00:12:03,355
Let's see.

170
00:12:05,094 --> 00:12:07,269
- Hmm.
- I know, I know.

171
00:12:07,356 --> 00:12:09,269
A 37.

172
00:12:10,791 --> 00:12:13,791
Oh, I don't know
what to do anymore.

173
00:12:15,835 --> 00:12:18,401
It could have been worse.

174
00:12:18,445 --> 00:12:20,837
You almost got the "A".

175
00:12:20,880 --> 00:12:23,576
