985
01:18:48,833 --> 01:18:50,788
You've got a way with words.

986
01:18:50,832 --> 01:18:52,833
You want to be in a play?

987
01:18:55,877 --> 01:18:57,834
What's all that shite?

988
01:18:59,965 --> 01:19:02,443
Nothing.

989
01:19:02,487 --> 01:19:04,617
I just think
you're right for the part.

990
01:19:21,751 --> 01:19:25,012
I always wanted to be
in one of your fucking plays.

