he tried to raise piranhas.

1071
01:26:02,173 --> 01:26:03,738
Yeah, I know he did.

1072
01:26:03,782 --> 01:26:06,956
- What did you think, Mr. Littlejeans?
- Best play ever, man.

1073
01:26:09,522 --> 01:26:11,479
I thought it was
a very realistic performance.

1074
01:26:11,523 --> 01:26:14,523
Yeah? Fischer stepped
over half my bloody lines.

1075
01:26:14,610 --> 01:26:16,567
That's funny.
I didn't notice.

1076
01:26:16,653 --> 01:26:19,219
Mr. Blume, how are Ronny and Donny
enjoying military school?

1077
01:26:19,263 --> 01:26:21,872
- They love it.
- Lucky bastards.

1078
01:26:21,960 --> 01:26:26,612
- I understand you're a neurosurgeon.
