1080
01:26:34,527 --> 01:26:36,831
You were incredible tonight, Margaret.

1081
01:26:36,875 --> 01:26:40,092
- You were that poor girl.
- Thank you.

1082
01:26:40,180 --> 01:26:43,877
I loved it when you grabbed onto the
bottom of the chopper as it was taking off.

1083
01:26:43,921 --> 01:26:45,876
- That was totally improvised.
- I know.

1084
01:26:45,920 --> 01:26:47,877
- Can I ask you a question?
- Of course.

1085
01:26:47,921 --> 01:26:50,443
Can you do
an Australian accent?

1086
01:26:50,486 --> 01:26:53,051
I'm working on something
that's set in the outback.

1087
01:26:53,095 --> 01:26:56,052
